data.description: A little Gem in a quiet community with pool! LOW HOA!! X Flood zone. This 3+Loft /2 bath townhouse offers a nice screened in Lania, remodeled bathrooms, granite tops in kitchen, newer SS appliances, NEW ROOF & A/C. It's conveniently located near FSW, Hospitals, RSW International airport, grocery stores, malls, great restaurants, and our beautiful SWFL beaches.   Perfect Investment/Winter Retreat/Starter Home. Don't miss your opportunity! Schedule a showing today.
